featured_reviews.review_id:
Assalam Alikum Wa rahmatullahi Wa Barkatuhu,
Dear Masjid Management and Residents of Pernumbet district
I'am Khazi Mohammed Zahiruddin just for introduction.
. With population of 100.000 approx.2011. And this is year 2020. Well
I'am taking this opportunity to write few words after seeing Masjid Jamiah after searching in google maps, MashaAllah small town having approx. 27 masajids in 2020. May Allah protect Imaan people of pernumbet. I personally visited this small town back in 1974 alongwith one of my cousin Brother (Anwarullah) who took me to relative Qazi Qayyum Saheb  during that time I could see series of tamarind trees along with the road side, surely not the same. Why I'am writing all these because from my childhood heard every single day "Pernumbet" thru my Dadima her name was "HURMATUNISSA BEGUM'. and she used to visit her birthplace which is Pernumbet. All my predecessor from this place which I cannot deny. Well long story short my Grand Father name "Qazi Mohammed Zahiruddin" his father name was Qazi Mohammed Ghouse Mohiuddin all from Pernumbet. During Nizam period migrated to Hyderabad Deccan alongwith "Barrister Ameen" later given title Jung by Nizam. Well most of our relatives in Hyderabad Deccan, some in Middle East and few in North America.This review to have a archive one who knows some of my family lineage take look at it. Please remember in your duaa. World is small.
Assalam Alikum
ZM
